properties.content:
L
library_add_check BEM-VINDO A PLATAFORMA LEGAL

Com a implementação da nova solução de workflow a Plataforma Legal tem como principais objetivos:

  • Alinhamento de processos/ procedimentos entre todas as operativas

  • Eliminação total de emails com documentação como ferramenta de trabalho primária

  • Informação de gestão atualizada e de rápida análise (eliminando diversos controlos manuais de cada operativa)

  • Foco em tarefas de maior valor acrescentado através da robotização e automatização de tarefas rotineiras e sem valor acrescentado

  • Segurança de informação pela centralização de informação numa única plataforma tecnológica com acesso restrito

  • Escalabilidade para outros serviços (idênticos aos já prestados)

<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        let button = sessionStorage.getItem("button");
        
        let novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/processo1?";
        let paramString = document.referrer.split('?')[1];
        let queryString = new URLSearchParams(paramString);
            
        for (let pair of queryString.entries()) {
            if(pair[0] != '_action'){
                novoUrl += pair[0] + "=" + pair[1] + "&";
            }
        }
        
        if(button === 'guardar'){
            window.location.href = novoUrl;
            //window.history.back();
        } else if(button === 'tabChange'){
            window.location.href = novoUrl;
        }
        
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("button");
        
        $("#filters_list_processo input[type = submit]").val("FILTRAR");
        
        $("p.msg").text("Por favor insira os filtros de pesquisa");
        
    });
</script>

        flag = true;
    } else {
        flag = false;

    if("#currentUser.groups.name#".split(";").includes(escalar)){
        mostrarBotoes();
    } else if ("#currentUser.department.name#".split(";").includes(escalar)){

     $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]").val(escalarProcesso).change();
    
    /*
    if(flag){
       
    } else {
        $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]").val(escalarProcesso + valorSelect).change();
    }*/
    
}

function esconderBotoes(){
    
    var inputs = $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]");
        for(var i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++) {
            inputs[i].disabled = true;
        }
        
        var options = $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]").children();
        for(var i = 0; i < options.length; i++) {
            options[i].disabled = true;
        }
}

function mostrarBotoes(){
    
    var inputs = $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]");
        for(var i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++) {
            inputs[i].disabled = false;
        }
        
        var options = $("select[name=multiPaged_1_menuPrincipal2_escalar_processo]").children();
        for(var i = 0; i < options.length; i++) {
            options[i].disabled = false;
        }
}
</script>

properties.sql:
SELECT ql.c_tipo_documento AS Tipo, COUNT(docs.id) AS Erros
FROM app_fd_processos pro
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_processo det ON pro.c_detalhe_processo = det.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_docs_processo docs ON docs.id = pro.c_docs
LEFT JOIN app_fd_check_op_reg_qual ql ON ql.c_fk = docs.id
WHERE ql.c_validacao_qual = 'NOK'
GROUP BY ql.c_tipo_documento

<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        var apiKey = "#envVariable.apiKeyReecaminhamentoProcessos#";
        var apiId = "#envVariable.apiIdReencaminhamentoProcessos#";
        
        let previousPage = sessionStorage.getItem("previousPage");
        let previousNWf = sessionStorage.getItem("nwf");
        let servico = sessionStorage.getItem("servico");
        if(previousPage === "importar"){
            var urlServico = "";
            if(servico === 'ch'){
                urlServico = "/jw/api/list/list_assignment?pageSize=1";
            }else if(servico === 'procu'){
                urlServico = "/jw/api/list/list_assignment_procu?pageSize=1";
            }else if(servico === 'hip' || servico === 'lea'){
                 urlServico = "/jw/api/list/list_assigment_hip_lea?pageSize=1";
            }else if(servico === 'dist'){
                 urlServico = "/jw/api/list/list_assignment_Dist?pageSize=1";
            }
            var assignmentId = "";
            var isAssigned = "1";
            $.ajax({
                    beforeSend: function(request){
                       request.setRequestHeader("api_key",apiKey);
                        request.setRequestHeader("api_id",apiId);
                    },
                    dataType: "json",
                    url: urlServico,   //list?sort=dateCreated&sortDescending=true&pageSize=1", //
                    success: function(data){
                        //console.log(data);
                        $.each(data.data,function(i,d){
                            assignmentId=d.activityId;
                            if(!d.nwfbanco.includes(previousNWf)){
                                isAssigned = "0";
                                //console.log("N√£o CONTEM O NWFBANCO");
                            }
                            
                        });
                    },
                    complete: function(){
                        novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/filaTrabalho?_mode=assignment&activityId=" + assignmentId; 
                        if(isAssigned ==="0"){
                            novoUrl= "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/ListaFilaTrabalho";
                        
                            
                        }
                        window.location.href = novoUrl;
                    }
                });
            
            
        } else if(previousPage === "redirectRegistos"){
                let novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/ListaFilaTrabalho";
                
                window.location.href = novoUrl;
                console.log("ENTROU REDIRECT REGISTOS");
        } else{
            let button = sessionStorage.getItem("button");
            
            let novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/filaTrabalho?";
            let paramString = document.referrer.split('?')[1];
            let queryString = new URLSearchParams(paramString);
                
            for (let pair of queryString.entries()) {
                if(pair[0] != '_action'){
                    novoUrl += pair[0] + "=" + pair[1] + "&";
                }
            }
            let processId= sessionStorage.getItem("assignmentProcessId");
            
            
            if(button === 'guardar'){
                window.location.href = novoUrl;
                console.log("ENTROU GUARDAR");
                //window.history.back();
            } else if (button === 'proximaAtividade' ){
                let flagRedirect = sessionStorage.getItem("redirect");
                var assignmentId = "";
                var regexGetProcessType = /workflowPL_(.*)/;
                var processType = processId.match(regexGetProcessType)[1];
    
                $.ajax({
                    beforeSend: function(request){
                       request.setRequestHeader("api_key",apiKey);
                        request.setRequestHeader("api_id",apiId);
                    },
                    dataType: "json",
                    url: "/jw/api/process/" + processType + "/listActivities/"+processId+"?sort=state&sortDescending=true&pageSize=1",
                    success: function(data){
                        $.each(data,function(i,d){
                            assignmentId=d.id;
                        });
                    },
                    complete: function(){
                        if(flagRedirect==="1"){
                            novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/filaTrabalho?_mode=assignment&activityId=" + assignmentId;
                        }else{
                            novoUrl = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/ListaFilaTrabalho";
                        }
                        window.location.href = novoUrl;
                    }
                });
               
              //.Criar nome do processo dinamico para chamar a API
            }else if(button === 'tabChange'){
                window.location.href = novoUrl;
            } else{
                window.location.href = "#request.scheme#://#request.serverName#:#request.serverPort##request.contextPath#/web/userview/workflowPL/UV_PL_Geral/_/ListaFilaTrabalho";
            }
            
            
        }
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("button");
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("assignmentProcessId");
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("redirect");
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("previousPage");
        window.sessionStorage.removeItem("nwf");
